      "width": 263.671875,
      "height": 112.5,
      "text": "File Structure:\nevidence/\n\u251c\u2500\u2500 evidence.config.yaml (dark theme)\n\u251c\u2500\u2500 sources/snowflake/connection.yaml\n\u251c\u2500\u2500 patches/@evidence-dev+core-*.patch\n\u251c\u2500\u2500 package.json (postinstall: patch-package)\n\u2514\u2500\u2500 src/pages/\n    \u251c\u2500\u2500 index.md  (main dashboard)\n    \u2514\u2500\u2500 +layout.svelte (custom theme)",
      "originalText": "File Structure:\nevidence/\n\u251c\u2500\u2500 evidence.config.yaml (dark theme)\n\u251c\u2500\u2500 sources/snowflake/connection.yaml\n\u251c\u2500\u2500 patches/@evidence-dev+core-*.patch\n\u251c\u2500\u2500 package.json (postinstall: patch-package)\n\u2514\u2500\u2500 src/pages/\n    \u251c\u2500\u2500 index.md  (main dashboard)\n    \u2514\u2500\u2500 +layout.svelte (custom theme)",
