    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "d_ai_evidence_text",
      "x": 1030,
      "y": 2030,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 150,
      "text": "Evidence.dev Rendering:\n\n```sql narrative\nselect narrative_text, model_id\nfrom snowflake.mart_season_narrative\nwhere season = ${inputs.season.value}\n  and constructor_id = '${inputs.constructor}'\n  and driver_1_code || '|' || driver_2_code\n      = '${inputs.pairing.value}'\n```\n\n{@html narrative[0].narrative_text}\n\nAI Season Story card with model_id footer\nHidden gracefully if no narrative exists",
      "originalText": "Evidence.dev Rendering:\n\n```sql narrative\nselect narrative_text, model_id\nfrom snowflake.mart_season_narrative\nwhere season = ${inputs.season.value}\n  and constructor_id = '${inputs.constructor}'\n  and driver_1_code || '|' || driver_2_code\n      = '${inputs.pairing.value}'\n```\n\n{@html narrative[0].narrative_text}\n\nAI Season Story card with model_id footer\nHidden gracefully if no narrative exists",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "strokeColor": "#22c55e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
