      "text": "Airflow DAG Task Order:\n  detect_rounds → ingest_rounds → dbt_run\n  → generate_narratives → dbt_run_narratives\n  → trigger_evidence_build\n\nGraceful skip if ANTHROPIC_API_KEY not set",
