      "text": "GitHub Pages \u2705 LIVE\n\nURL: singhpriyanshu5.github.io\n     /f1-rivalry-dashboard/\n\nStatic site: all Snowflake data\nbaked in at build time\n\nCI: npm ci \u2192 postinstall \u2192\n  patch-package applies patches\n  \u2192 npm run sources \u2192 build\n  \u2192 deploy to Pages",
